  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      <h1 class="display-4 fw-extrabold mb-3">Shipping <span class="text-primary">Policy</span></h1>
      <p class="text-muted fs-5 mb-5">Learn about our premium shipping methods, delivery partners, and high-quality protective packaging.</p>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-box-seam text-primary me-2"></i> Our Signature Packaging</h3>
        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">
          At ToyBerry, we understand that luxury toys require luxury protection. Every order is meticulously hand-packed in our signature, eco-friendly ToyBerry gift boxes. We use heavy-duty, double-walled corrugated cardboard and customized protective inserts to ensure your purchases arrive in pristine, showroom condition.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-truck text-primary me-2"></i> Domestic Shipping Tiers (India)</h3>
        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">We partner with premium courier services including BlueDart, Delhivery, and FedEx to provide secure, rapid delivery.</p>
        
        <div class="row g-4 mt-2">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 h-100">
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                <span class="badge bg-primary-subtle text-primary rounded-pill px-3 py-1">Standard Delivery</span>
                <span class="fw-bold text-dark">₹250</span>
              </div>
              <h5 class="fw-bold">Free on Orders above ₹5,000</h5>
              <p class="text-muted small mb-0 mt-2">Delivery within 3 to 5 business days across major cities. Fully trackable.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 h-100">
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                <span class="badge bg-secondary-subtle text-secondary rounded-pill px-3 py-1">Express Shipping</span>
                <span class="fw-bold text-dark">₹499</span>
              </div>
              <h5 class="fw-bold">Next-Day Delivery</h5>
              <p class="text-muted small mb-0 mt-2">Guaranteed next-day delivery for metropolitan zones. Orders must be placed before 2 PM IST.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-clock-history text-primary me-2"></i> Processing Times</h3>
        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">
          Orders are processed and dispatched within 24 hours of payment verification (excluding Sundays and national holidays). As soon as your order leaves our Mumbai fulfillment center, a dispatch email containing your unique tracking link and invoice copy will be sent.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-geo-alt text-primary me-2"></i> Shipping Restrictions</h3>
        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">
          Please note that we currently ship only within India. We do not deliver to P.O. boxes or military addresses. A signature is required upon delivery for all orders to ensure security and prevent packages from being left unattended.
        </p>
      </div>
